// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0021 — Mass File Rename (akira)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 79a67f4f-70ce-5122-b92b-12e74517c81e

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
